---
import Layout from "@/layouts/Layout.astro";
import {formatOrdinals} from "@/utils/formatOrdinals";
---

<Layout title="JavaZone 2024 Partner">
    <main>
        <section>
            <h1>Partner</h1>
            <h2>Partner meeting</h2>
            <p>Video from partner meeting December 5th</p>
            <p><a href="https://vimeo.com/891500045/7df20a26e4">Video on vimeo</a></p>
            <p><a href="https://www.dropbox.com/scl/fi/wivcmqsj9a5058p8s3qcj/JZ2024PartnermeetingOne.pdf?rlkey=48d1t09xcfjqts9kfytk7aegb&dl=0">Slides</a></p>
            <h1>Partner registration</h1>
            <p>Partner registration opens <b>January 15th 2024 at 10:00</b> Registration is done by using the a link on this page.</p>
            <p>Even though all partners are considered equal, there are a few options to choose from. There is a base package that everyone gets, and then there are a few available expansions. Note that these expansions have limited availability.</p>
            <p>Partner packages (both the standard package and the expansion options) are sold first come first served starting January 15th and as long as there are still packages left.</p>
            <h1>Partner packages</h1>
            <h2>Standard package</h2>
            <h3>Stand</h3>
            <p>6 square meters (3x2) with back and side wall, in the main conference hall.</p>
            <h3>Profiling</h3>
            <p>Logo with link on homepage and profiling in Oslo Spectrum</p>
            <h3>Stand ticket</h3>
            <p>4 flexible tickets for stand personnel.</p>
            <h3>Particiant tickets</h3>
            <p>Partner price on tickets for your colleagues</p>
            <h3>Price</h3>
            <p><b>95 000,- NOK ex VAT</b></p>
            <h2>Concept stand</h2>
            <p>All the benefits of the standard package with a stand of 48 square meters (8X6 m) stand</p>
            <p>Large space for showing off your own concept</p>
            <h3>Additional price</h3>
            <p><b>78 000,- NOK ex VAT</b></p>
            <h2>Restaurant stand</h2>
            <p>All the benefits of the standard package with a restaurant stand</p>
            <p>24 square meters (6x4 m) with a connected restaurant</p>
            <p>Contious food serving from your stand throughout the conference.</p>
            <p>Menu in cooperation with event partners.</p>
            <h1>Partner tickets</h1>
            <p>Order from March 1st until May 15th</p>
            <p>Round robin distribution on tickets ordered by May 15th</p>
            <p>First come first served if tickets are still left after May 15th</p>
            <p><b>Price: 7.990,- NOK Ex. VAT</b></p>

            
            
        </section>
    </main>
</Layout>

<style>
    body {
        background-image: url("../images/main-area.jpg");
        backdrop-filter: blur(3px);
    }

    main {
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 3rem;
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: center;
    }

    section {
        display: grid;
        gap: 1rem;
        padding: 2rem;
        background: wheat;
        color: black;
        box-shadow: 1px 1px 1000px lightgray;
    }

    h1 {
        font-size: 3rem;
    }
    h2 {
        font-size: 2rem;
    }
    h3 {
        font-size: 1.5rem;
    }
</style>
